        <item>
          <title>Amazon Removes Download & Transfer via USB Option on Kindles - Restricting User Flexibility</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Amazon is removing the Download & Transfer via USB option on Kindles, effective February 26. This means users will no longer be able to download ebooks purchased from Amazon and move them to their Kindle over a wired USB connection.]]></description>
